import React from "react"; import imgSlide1 from "../../assets/images/slides/home-bg-1.jpg"; import imgSlide2 from "../../assets/images/slides/home-bg-2.jpg"; import imgDummy from "../../assets/images/dummy.png"; import imgMacbook from "../../assets/images/macbookpro.png"; import imgIpad from "../../assets/images/ipad.png"; import imgIphone from "../../assets/images/ihpone.png"; import imgAstro from "../../assets/images/astro-img.png"; import imgPlanet from "../../assets/images/planet-img.png"; import imgPlanet2 from "../../assets/images/planet-img-2.png"; import imgPlanet3 from "../../assets/images/planet-img-3.png"; import imgScreen from "../../assets/images/screen1_content.jpg"; import imgScreen2 from "../../assets/images/screen2_content.jpg"; import imgScreen3 from "../../assets/images/screen3_content.png"; import Icofont from "react-icofont"; const HeroStudio = () => (
  • OUR DESIGN COLORFUL LIKE NATURE
    When you come across someone colorful and vibrant maybe in the present it isn't so interesting, but, in the past, it sheds a wonderful light onto living life.
  • RESPONSIVE
    FOR MOBILE PERFECTION
    Our Sliders dont just look great on desktop devices, but scale down beautifully to work on mobile devices like smartphones or tablets.
); export default HeroStudio;
